'''北鮭屬'''（'''''Stenodus'''''），為[[鮭科|鮭科]]的其中一[[屬|屬]]，是淡水鮭魚，其下有兩種，但有時白北鮭也被當做[[極北鮭|極北鮭]]（''Stenodus leucichthys''）的亞種。<ref name="Belyaeva">{{cite web|first=E. S.|last=Belyaeva|url=http://www.caspianenvironment.org/biodb/eng/fishes/Stenodus%20leucichthys%20leucichthys/main.htm|title=''Stenodus leucichthys leucichthys''|publisher=caspianenvironment.org|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120227145632/http://www.caspianenvironment.org/biodb/eng/fishes/Stenodus%20leucichthys%20leucichthys/main.htm|archivedate=2012-02-27|accessdate=2013-09-22}}</ref><ref name="IUCN leucichthys">{{IUCN|IUCN_Year=2011|author=Freyhof, J.; and Kottelat, M.|year=2008|ID=20745|title=Stenodus leucichthys}}</ref>

該屬的魚雖然有獨特的捕食形態，但是在[[系統發生學|系統發生學]]上與[[白鮭屬|白鮭屬]]（''Coregonus''）區別不大。<ref name=BCD>Bernatchez L, Colombani F, Dodson JJ (1991) [http://www.bio.ulaval.ca/labdodson/Papers%20Julian/Bernatchez_1991_JFB.pdf Phylogenetic relationships among the subfamily Coregoninae as revealed by mitochondrial DNA restriction analysis] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bio.ulaval.ca/labdodson/Papers%20Julian/Bernatchez_1991_JFB.pdf |date=20130927031704 }} ''Journal of Fish Biology'' 39 (Suppl A):283-290.</ref>

